3622
03:39:55,080 --> 03:39:59,900
Memory is handed out in chunks called pages, typically 4 kilobytes each, but what's really

3623
03:39:59,900 --> 03:40:04,040
interesting is that each process gets its own page table, and that means two applications

3624
03:40:04,040 --> 03:40:06,340
